node.text:
“You know how dogs will scratch at the air when you hit ✨that itchy spot✨? Well, Pudge nibbles at the air when you scratch her itchy armpits. 
I showed this little quirk of hers to her vet and he literally told me she had ✨itchy armpits✨ 😂💀 
She loves to be brushed so much 💕 I love how she lets me lift up her arm to get at her itchy pits” #catsofinstagram

node.text:
What enabled you to share joy this past year? We talk with @chewy around 2020 and what it means to be a Joymaker! 🎁✨

GIVEAWAY // 
To enter: 
- Share a video of your cat
- Tag @Chewy + @cats_of_instagram 
- with the hashtag #ChewyJoymakers

We’ll feature the winner’s video on our Instagram and hook you and your kitty up with goodies!
#sponsored #catsofinstagram
